    "description": {
      "value": "<p>The Hitosashi Clan are famous for their dancing and unique styles of combat revolving around their art of dance. They primarily focus on Taijutsu and genjutsu styles of combat and are a very unique clan.</p><p><b>Source:</b> Mechanics/Character_Options/Occupations/Community Compendium/Hitosashi Clan.md</p><p><b>Category:</b> Community Compendium</p><p><b>Prerequisite:</b> Age 8+</p><p><b>Fixed Class Skills:</b> Perform (dance).</p><p><b>Class Skills:</b> Select 2 from Balance, Chakra Control, Genjutsu, Hide, Knowledge (art), Knowledge (ninja lore), Ninjutsu, Taijutsu.</p><p><b>Feat:</b> Select one from Acrobatic, Advanced Bloodline (Buruhada), Combat Martial Arts, Creative, Defensive Martial Arts, Genjutsu Adept, Genin, Genius Ninja, Nin Weapons Proficiency, Taijutsu Adept, Tenodori.</p><p><b>Wealth Bonus Increase:</b> +1</p><p><b>Reputation Bonus Increase:</b> +1</p><p><b>Affiliation:</b> You require 1 less success to learn Tenodori techniques.</p>"
